de.sciss.jcollider
Class Group

java.lang.Object
  de.sciss.jcollider.Node
      de.sciss.jcollider.Group
All Implemented Interfaces:
Constants, TreeNode
public class Group
extends Node

Mimics SCLang's Group class, that is, it's a client side representation of a group in the synthesis graph

Version:
0.23, 02-Oct-05
Author:
Hanns Holger Rutz
Warning:
this is a quick direct translation from SClang which is largely untested. before all methods have been thoroughly verified, excepted some of them to be wrong or behave different than expected. what certainly works is instantiation, new- and free-messages
